content: HashWarlock: Merged 5 PRs this month, with significant contributions to the TEE feature (PR #3512, +826/-217 lines) and fixing plugin installation issues (PR #3451, +18464/-6337 lines). Fixed several critical bugs including CLI build commands (PR #3378), core build targeting (PR #3371), and package upgrades to resolve errors (PR #3146). Created 3 issues (all now closed) related to TEE plugin test coverage, character file storage, and public key security, while also providing reviews and comments on other contributors' work.
